    <lb n="1r-11"/>ni haji</roleName></persName> hasa ro ma di ko, <persName type="human"><roleName type="datu" subtype="guru">Guru so dupaṅano·ni haji</persName></roleName> datu paro·ta<unclear>n</unclear>
