    <lb n="1r-14" break="no"/>hati·</placeName>, hasa ro ma di ko,<persName type="human"><roleName type="datu">Datu Paṁguhala·ni haji ho</persName></roleName>. Iya, gohara· maram
    <lb n="1r-15" break="no"/>⌉o·puni <persName type="human"><roleName type="datu" subtype="ompu-tuvan"><choice><orig>hopu</orig><reg>Hompu</reg></choice>Tuvana· Binaru· kata ni haji</persName></roleName> datu paro·tan·daṁ bolan
    <lb n="1r-16" break="no"/>⌉o· ganapu· desa liyata· paro·tibi sumarikano· homasa· siguma
