  <p rend="1-7">
    <p> Teaching/Instruction of the core of the mountain-oracle [to be observed] either during the ceremony (horja) Sita-sita,
      or people make us into datu during a great war, or people make us into datu in inaugurating a new settlement, or we are celebrating a marriage,
      or we are offering unhusked rice on the rice field for the feast-giving group, or we are bringing our child to the river,
      or during the porsahan [ceremony] of the man who died old, or during the magic warfare. </p>
    </p>
